                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Welcome to Officio – your online client file management and business software solution! </p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Officio empowers you to successfully manage your day-to-day activities, comply with your regulatory requirements, and grow your immigration/citizenship practice through its industry-specific modules, customizable features and educational resources.</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">For help on how to use your Officio account, please review the following <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Get Started</strong> resources:</p><ol style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q308\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Add a Client</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q309\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Add a Case</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q192\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Add a Form</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q189\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Add a Note to the Client File</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q184\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Create a Client-Specific Task</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q205\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Create a Payment Schedule</a></li><li style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q310\" class=\"blulinkun\">How to Use Officio Studio</a></li></ol><p>For a more in-depth introduction to Officio's modules and features, please view our <a href=\"/help/index/index?type=help#q29\" class=\"blulinkun\"><strong>Video Demonstrations</strong></a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;ma