                "question"              => "What is Uniques Software Corp.?",
                "answer"                => "<p>Serving since 1996, <em>Uniques Software Corp.</em> has established itself as the largest software provider in the Canadian immigration/citizenship industry, offering a variety of products designed and built to improve productivity.</p>\n\n<p>As the IT leader in the immigration/citizenship industry, we work closely with industry experts, as well as regulatory bodies, to ensure compliance with the latest regulatory requirements. </p>",
