            array(
                "faq_id"                => 54,
                "faq_section_id"        => 44,
                "question"              => "Is my data secure in Officio?",
                "answer"                => "<p>The security of your data is of utmost importance to us. We use ISO 17799 protocol, which is the highest security protocol used in the banking and medical industry. We also use several security tiers to protect the hardware, software and overall network.  </p>\n\n<p>In addition to this, we have incremental backups every six hours. That is, in a 24-hour period, we have four incremental backups and one full nightly backup.</p>",
