                "question"              => "What is Enhanced Task Management?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Enhanced Task Management</strong> is the ability to send and receive reminder messages between multiple users. </p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Tasks can be assigned to specific users and each action taken on the task can be documented in the client file. Through this feature, users can collaborate on a particular task and the supervising user can monitor the progress of the task.</p>",
