            ),
            array(
                "faq_id"                => 66,
                "faq_section_id"        => 57,
                "question"              => "How do I send an automated thank you when a prospect completes an assessment form?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">To send an automatic thank you message when a prospect completes an assessment form:</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2011-17-27%202ee9d8a8ab772044d1fc.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2011-17-27%202ee9d8a8ab772044d1fc.png\" /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2013-35-29%203cc5df0686cda77f486e.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2013-35-29%203cc5df0686cda77f486e.png\" /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2013-17-44%2047d0ae3912e8caadbc53.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2013-17-44%2047d0ae3912e8caadbc53.png\" /></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2013-18-20%201d83036c159d94505caa.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2013-18-20%201d83036c159d94505caa.png\" /></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2013-21-10%20e1e9c43ab2c57dc90279.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2013-21-10%20e1e9c43ab2c57dc90279.png\" /></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-17%2013-24-52%20d9e98417fd6489c4affc.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-06-17%2013-24-52%20d9e98417fd6489c4affc.png\" /></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><li>Go to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Admin</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Prospects Manager</strong>.</li><li>Select the questionnaire for which you would like to send an automated thank you message upon completion by the prospect.</li><li>Click <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Edit Questionnaire</strong> or double click on the questionnaire.</li><li>Under <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Automated Responses</strong>, select the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Thank you</strong> template next to the relevant category of immigration.</li><li>Click on<strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"> Save changes</strong>.</li><li>Go to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Prospect Templates</strong> (under <strong>Menu </strong>or <strong>Quick Menu</strong>).</li><li>Select the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Thank you</strong> template. </li><li>Click on<strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"> Edit Template</strong> or double click on the <strong>Thank you</strong> template.</li><li>Click on <strong>Define </strong><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Settings</strong>.</li><li>Type your email address in the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">BCC </strong>field.</li><li>Click on <strong>Define Content</strong>.</li><li>Edit the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Thank You</strong> template, as needed.</li><li>Click <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Save</strong>.</li><li>Test the automated notification setting by filling out the questionnaire.</li></ol>",
