                "question"              => "How to Work on and Track a General Task",
                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>To Work on and Track a General Task:</strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Click on <strong>My Tasks</strong>.</span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select the <strong>General Task</strong> to be worked <span style=\"color:#000000;\">on. </span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">You can now edit, reply, or mark the task as complete.</span></span></li>\n</ol>",
