dit your new document</span>.<span style=\"color:#000000;\"> b) If a template was used, </span></em><span style=\"color:#000000;\">officio </span><em><span style=\"color:#000000;\">will automatically populate the customized fields with the relevant information from the client’s profile.</span></em></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
