                "faq_section_id"        => 51,
                "question"              => "How to Manage a Document or File",
                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>To Manage a Document or File:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>My Documents</strong>.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Right-click on the document or file you want to manage.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>Select all</strong> to select the contents of all folders.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Preview </em>to <strong>Preview </strong>the selected document or file. </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Download </em>to Download the document or file.  </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under<em> Download as ZIP</em>  to either <strong>Download All as ZIP</strong>, including all documents/files in all folders, or to only <strong>Download this folder files as ZIP</strong>, which will only include the documents/files in the selected folder. </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Rename </em>to <strong>Rename </strong>the selected folder. </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Delete </em>to <strong>Delete </strong>the selected folder. </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Send to Inbox</em><em> </em>to send the document or file to an Inbox. </span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Move to</em> to move a document or file to another location.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Follow the steps outlined under <em>Copy to</em><em> </em>to copy a document or file to another location.</span></span></li>\n</ol>",
