                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>To <span style=\"color:#000000;\">Use Shared Workspace:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>My Documents</strong>.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select <strong>Shared Workspace</strong>.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>New Document</strong> or <strong>New File </strong>to create a new document or file or click <strong>Upload </strong>to add an existing document or file. <em>NOTE: <span style=\"color:#000000;\">Any document or file posted to <strong>Shared Workspace</strong><strong> </strong>will be visible to all users to whom you grant access.</span></em></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
