                "question"              => "How to Edit an Existing Email Account",
                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To Edit an Existing Email Account:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>Email</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>Settings</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select the email account you want to edit.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>Edit</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">See <strong>To Set-up/Edit General Settings</strong>, <strong>To Set-up/Edit Incoming Mail Server</strong>, or <strong>To Set-up/Edit Outgoing Mail Server (SMTP Mail Server) </strong>for information on how to <strong>Edit Email Account</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
