                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To Create a New Email Folder:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>Email</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>New Folder</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>New root folder</strong> to create a new root (or main) folder.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>New subfolder</strong> to create a new subfolder under a root (or main) folder.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
