                "question"              => "How to Change the Email Reading Pane",
                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To Change the Email Reading Pane:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>Email</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click the arrow next to <strong>Reading Pane</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select either:</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Bottom</span></span></strong></span></a><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> – </span>to have email preview appear at the bottom of the reading pane and the list of emails appear at the top of the reading pane.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Right</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"> – to have email preview appear to the right of the reading pane and the list of emails appear to the left of the reading pane.</spa