                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To Reply to an Email Message:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>Email</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong>Reply</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select the <strong>From</strong> (or return) email address. <em>(NOTE: This is necessary if you have more than one email account in </em>Officio<em> and want the email message to be sent from an account other than the default email account.)</em></span></span></span></a></span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Type your response in the space provided. <em>(NOTE: Once sent, </em>Officio<em> saves a copy of the message under the <strong>Documents</strong> section of the client’s file.)</em></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
