                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color:#373737;\">To Share a Template:</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong>Client Templates</strong>.</span></span></li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click and hold on the template you would like to share with other individuals from your <strong>My Templates</strong> folder and drag and drop it onto the <strong>Shared Templat<span style=\"color:#000000;\">es</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> folder. </span><a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><em>NOTE: Once the template is in the <strong>Shared Templates</strong> folder, it is automatically visible to all individuals to whom you have given shared access.</em></span></a></span></span></li>\n</ol>",
