                "question"              => "How to Invoice a Client",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To Invoice a Client:</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-15%2010-01-49%20941f264159bf86d52153.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-06-15%2010-01-49%20941f264159bf86d52153.jpg\" /></span></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-15%2010-18-30%2093987c80cb5da62049cb.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-06-15%2010-18-30%2093987c80cb5da62049cb.png\" /></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Clients</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select a client.</span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Accounting.</strong> </span></span></span></span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select one of the fees or disbursements that show</span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"> <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">DUE</strong><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"> Invoice Now</strong>.<br /></span></span></span></span></strong></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on<strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"> Invoice Now</strong>. <em>NOTES: 1) </em>Officio <em>will indicate <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">DUE</strong> <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Invoice now</strong> next to all transactions that are ready to be invoiced. 2) You can only invoice a payment for which there are fees due. If the amount is not yet due, </em>Officio <em>will notify you and suggest marking the amount as due today. If the amount has already been invoiced, </em>Officio<em> will advise you that it already has an invoice. 3) An invoice number will automatically be generated with the current date.</em></span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Under <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Generate Invoice</strong>, customize the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Invoice #</strong> and <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Date of Invoice</strong>, as needed. <em>NOTE: To change the entire Invoice Number, the \"Admin\" role can: 1) go to</em></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><em> <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Admin</strong></em></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><em>, 2) click </em></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><em>Company Details</em></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><em>, 3) </em></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">scroll down to </span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Invoice Number Settings</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">, and 4) edit the text in the</span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"> Format</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"> field.</span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></span></span></span></strong></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ensure the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Invoice </strong>template is selected.</span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Generate</strong>. <em>NOTE: Copies of the invoice will be emailed to you and to the client.</em></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><em><br /></em></strong></li></ol>",
