                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">To add a new case status, please follow the steps below:</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-18%2010-38-23%206de3e12175160112d824.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-06-18%2010-38-23%206de3e12175160112d824.png\" /></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><li>Go to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Admin</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Case Status</strong> under <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Manage Settings</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">+ New Status</strong>.</li><li>Type the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">New Status</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Save Changes</strong>.</li></ol>",
