            array(
                "faq_id"                => 263,
                "faq_section_id"        => 44,
                "question"              => "What are the refund and cancellation terms?",
                "answer"                => "<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">The following refund and cancellation terms can be found in our <strong>Terms of Use </strong>document (<span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#1155cc;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><a href=\"http://www.uniques.ca/terms\" class=\"blulinkun\">www.uniques.ca/terms</a>)</span></span></span>:</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><strong><em>J. TERMINATION OF SERVICE.</em></strong> </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">You may terminate your user account upon written notice to officio.ca at least 2 business days before your next billing date. Upon receipt of your cancellation, officio.ca will confirm your cancellation request by email. If you do not receive such email from officio.ca it means your initial request has not been received.  </span></span></span></span>Upon termination by officio.ca or at your direction, you may request a backup of your data, which officio.ca will make available to you. A charge of $250 will be applied to provide a backup to monthly subscribers. The backup fee is waived for annual subscribers. You must make such request at the notification of termination to receive such file within thirty (30) days of termination. Otherwise, ANY DATA YOU HAVE STORED ON officio.ca’S SYSTEMS MAY NOT BE RETRIEVED, and officio.ca shall have no obligation to maintain any data stored in your account or to forward any data to you or any third party.</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><strong><em>L. REFUND OF CHARGES. </em></strong> </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">All officio.ca services are prepaid for the period selected (monthly, yearly or otherwise) and are NON-REFUNDABLE. This includes accounts that are terminated prematurely in accordance with section J. </span></span></span></span></p>",
                "meta_tags"             => "administration\nsubscription\nplan\npolicy",
                "featured"              => "N",
                "content_type"          => "text",
