                "question"              => "Can I add more than one email account to my Officio account?",
                "answer"                => "<p>Yes. To add an additional email account to your <em>Officio </em>account:</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Go to <strong>Email</strong>.</li>\n\t<li>Click on <strong>Settings</strong>.</li>\n\t<li>Click on <strong>Add</strong>.</li>\n\t<li>Follow the steps outlined in the following articles: <strong>How to Add an Email Account</strong>, <strong>How to Set-up/Edit Email General Settings</strong>,<strong> How to Set-up/Edit Incoming Mail Server</strong>, and <strong>How to Set-up/Edit Outgoing Mail Server (SMTP Mail Server)</strong>.</li>\n</ol>",
