                "question"              => "How to Print Client File Notes",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">To print client <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">File Notes</strong>, follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Steps 1-4:</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-26%2016-31-30%2006f326cf8836a810abb4.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2022-01-26%2016-31-30%2006f326cf8836a810abb4.png\" /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><br /></p><p><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 5-8:</span></strong></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-27%2011-20-50%2077298859459fbc9f551c.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-27%2011-20-50%2077298859459fbc9f551c.png\" /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">NOTE: </span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Regarding <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Step 3</strong>, The <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Print </strong>feature will print whatever is visible in the reading pane. To print the details of the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">File Notes</strong>, first expand the file note you want to print so that they are visible in the reading pane.</span></em></p>",
