                "question"              => "What is Officio Studio?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>Officio Studio</em> is a cloud-based platform developed by <em>Uniques Software Corp</em>. that provides <em>Officio </em>users with free and all-inclusive access to:</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">1. Over a hundred hours of CPD content on various immigration and citizenship topics provided by recognized providers;<br />2. Client file simulations involving interactions between an authorized representative and clients with all the twists and complexities of their cases;<br />3. Weekly practical tips from industry experts; and<br />4. Inspiring courses and videos on a wide range of business topics, including entrepreneurship and customer service, as well as networking topics such as communication and building your professional network.  </p>",
