                "question"              => "What is the Dashboard?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">What is the Dashboard?</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Need to quickly monitor how your practice is doing and what’s happening in the immigration industry?</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>Dashboard</em> helps you stay on top of your tasks, deadlines and meetings and keeps you up-to-date on the most recent immigration news and changes.<br /><br /></p>",
