                "question"              => "What is the My Tasks module?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">What is the My Tasks module?</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Need help managing all of your tasks and deadlines<em>?</em></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>My Tasks</em> gives you control over your work so that you can set tasks and appointments for yourself and others, ensure those tasks are met, and fulfill your regulatory requirements to meet all applicable deadlines. </p>",
