                "question"              => "What is the My Email module?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">What is the My Email module?</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Need to easily send routine email messages to clients and ensure that all email communications are filed in the proper client file?</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>My Email </em>simplifies communicating with clients by allowing you to create and customize template messages, which can be sent to individual or multiple clients. All emails sent and received through <em>Email</em> are automatically filed in the relevant client file.  </p>",
