                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">What is the My Calendar module?</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Need to effectively schedule and manage appointments with clients and business contacts? </p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>My Calendar</em> helps you manage your time by sharing your calendar and viewing staff calendars in order to efficiently schedule meetings. It also enables you to set-up appointments with clients and business contacts.</p>",
