                "question"              => "What is the My Documents module?",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">What is the My Documents module?</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Need to collaborate with clients to securely receive large documents and ensure that all client documents are organized in the client file?</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em>My Documents</em> is a space for you to create, work on and store documents related to your practice. The <em>Shared Workspace</em> feature allows you to collaborate on particular documents with specific individuals.</p>",
