                "question"              => "How to Use Officio Studio",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Please watch the following introductory video on Officio Studio:</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/592753876/b44cc556ea\" class=\"blulinkun\">https://vimeo.com/592753876/b44cc556ea</a></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">To use Officio Studio, follow the steps below:</p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Steps 1-2:</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-09-09%2009-08-34%204c80596b943e43e4e067.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-09-09%2009-08-34%204c80596b943e43e4e067.png\" /></p><p>A. To watch a <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Simulation</strong>, follow the steps below:</p><p><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Steps 3-4:</strong></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-09-09%2009-09-13%2047f8067ab33a0d4fc5ed.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-09-09%2009-09-13%2047f8067ab33a0d4fc5ed.png\" /></p><p><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Steps 5-7:</strong><br /><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-09-09%2009-09-37%2016c691162d53b64c4b6d.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-09-09%2009-09-37%2016c691162d53b64c4b6d.png\" /></p><p>B. To watch a <strong>CPD Course (Valid)</strong>, follow the steps below:</p><p><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Steps 8-9:</strong></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-09-09%2009-11-02%20afbe87f62b8ae4f446a6.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\