p;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-09-09%2009-53-45%20311793a4589bf5eb6902.png\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>A CPD receipt will be issued to you, similar to the one below, which you can print or save in support of your regulatory requirements. </p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-09-09%2009-39-35%20f309e60d3d0a031cc2d8.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2021-09-09%2009-39-35%20f309e60d3d0a031cc2d8.png\" /></p><p><br /></p>",
