                "question"              => "How to Add a Client File Note (Advanced)",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">To add a client file note, follows the steps below:</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><br /></span></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://officiocav2test.s3.amazonaws.com/help_article_images/2021-06-02%2011-29-51.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" /></span></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"https://cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2021-06-07%2014-43-21%20371ca6d9b0225e9bec29.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2021-06-07%2014-43-21%20371ca6d9b0225e9bec29.jpg\" /></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Go to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Clients</strong>.</span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Select a client.</span></span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">File Notes.</strong> </span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">+ New Note</strong> to add a note to that particular client’s file (e.g., summary of a discussion with a client, final status update, etc.). <em>NOTE: Client tasks automatically appear under the <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">File Notes </strong>as tasks.</em></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Type your note in the space provided. </span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Check <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Visible to Client</strong> if you want that particular client to see the note. </span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Left-to-right </strong>to change the alignment of the text of the note to <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Right-to-left</strong>. </span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click on <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Attach Files</strong> to attach a file or document to the note.</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Click <strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Save </strong>to add the note to the client's file.</span></span></li></ol>",
