                "question"              => "How to Resolve a Blocked Gmail Connection",
                "answer"                => "<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">If <em>Gmail </em>has blocked your email connection, follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\">Steps 1-4:</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bolder;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-10%2015-11-01%20ebe8434b22c3f38d436d.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2022-01-10%2015-11-01%20ebe8434b22c3f38d436d.png\" /></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">NOTE: Ensure that you are logged out of all other email accounts.</span></em></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 5-6:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-10%2015-10-23%20ed353d9cf9ddaaa251f5.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;border-style:none;padding:0px 1px;\" alt=\"2022-01-10%2015-10-23%20ed353d9cf9ddaaa251f5.png\" /><br /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Steps 7-8:</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-10%2015-16-43%2056a9a367687b6a94a789.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-10%2015-16-43%2056a9a367687b6a94a789.png\" /></p><p><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">NOTE: Ensure that the access to less secure apps now indicates that it is <strong>ON</strong>.</span></em></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br /></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 9-10:</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-10%2015-28-06%207ee23782cd3a0cad2855.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-10%2015-28-06%207ee23782cd3a0cad2855.png\" /></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 11-16:</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-10%2016-15-31%20756a95af216228208792.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-10%2016-15-31%20756a95af216228208792.png\" /></span></strong></p><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">If you are using a <strong>POP3 Server Type</strong>, follow steps 17-22 below. If you are using an<strong> IMAP Server Type</strong>, follow steps 23-28 instead. For information on the difference between POP3 and IMAP, review the Help topic titled: <a href=\"http://help/index/index?type=help#q330\" class=\"blulinkun\">What's the Difference Between POP3 and IMAP Server Types</a>.</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 17-22:</span></strong></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-11%2009-55-43%2073b55d93635e2dcae33d.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-11%2009-55-43%2073b55d93635e2dcae33d.png\" /></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 23-28:</span></strong></p><p><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-11%2009-57-35%20c28470497fc825798608.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-11%2009-57-35%20c28470497fc825798608.png\" /></p><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">If you are using a <strong>POP3 </strong>Server Type, follow steps 29-36 below. If you are using an <strong>IMAP </strong>Server Type, follow steps 37-44 instead. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Steps 29-36:</strong></span></p><p><strong><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-11%2010-13-06%20f2acc3bf00b65a15d6fc.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-11%2010-13-06%20f2acc3bf00b65a15d6fc.png\" /></strong></p><p><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">NOTE: Upon clicking on <strong>Test Account Settings</strong>, you should receive a test message to your original webmail account and to your </span></em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Officio </span><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">account.</span></em><strong></strong></p><p><strong><br /></strong></p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Steps 37-44:</span></strong><img src=\"//cahelpcenter.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/content_images/0/2022-01-11%2010-25-09%20916b3503120532dbadd5.png\" style=\"vertical-align:top;margin:5px auto;text-align:center;\" alt=\"2022-01-11%2010-25-09%20916b3503120532dbadd5.png\" /><p><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">NOTE: Upon clicking on <strong>Test Account Settings</strong>, you should receive a test message to your original webmail account and to your </span></em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Officio </span><em><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">account.</span></em></p>",
